re of human communication and perception, and\nhow we interact with information and data. It will revolutionize the future of\nhow we work, learn, play and entertain, receive medical care, and socialize.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 2 Nov 2021 01:42:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-11-09"}
